525,"센트럴 파크, 뉴욕",모리스 브라질 프렌더개스트,유화,,,https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src=%22https%3A%2F%2Fdbscthumb-phinf.pstatic.net%2F3329_000_93%2F20141110102342731_3L8HNMQ9X.jpg%2F2011021817425414.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw690_fst%26wm%3DN%22&twidth=690&theight=461&opts=17,
526,아비뇽 교황청,폴 시냐크,유화,캔버스에 유채(Huile sur toile),신인상주의,https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src=%22https%3A%2F%2Fdbscthumb-phinf.pstatic.net%2F3329_000_1%2F20140912092054328_E03N49OOK.jpg%2F06-532537.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw690_fst_n%26wm%3DY%22&twidth=667&theight=530&opts=17,
