537,미의 3여신,지오반니 안토니오 바치 소도마,소묘,"회색지, 흰 부분 강조, 펜 (데생), 갈색 수채, 갈색 잉크(papier gris, rehauts de blanc, plume (dessin), lavis brun, encre brune)",르네상스,https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src=%22https%3A%2F%2Fdbscthumb-phinf.pstatic.net%2F3329_000_22%2F20140924060739968_BT4AV8CEQ.jpg%2F05-509854.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw690_fst_n%26wm%3DY%22&twidth=358&theight=530&opts=17,
