719,지구를 받치고 있는 헤라클레스,안니발레 카라치,소묘,"베이지색 종이, 흰부분 강조, 흑석(papier beige,rehauts de blanc,pierre noire,)",,https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src=%22https%3A%2F%2Fdbscthumb-phinf.pstatic.net%2F3329_000_1%2F20140916003141432_XHRCKO4TR.jpg%2F94-059891.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw690_fst_n%26wm%3DY%22&twidth=690&theight=451&opts=17,
