818,랑발 공주,루이 카로지,소묘,"붉은 안료, 과슈, 흑연, 수채화(sanguine, gouache, mine de plomb, aquarelle)",,https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src=%22https%3A%2F%2Fdbscthumb-phinf.pstatic.net%2F3329_000_8%2F20140919170347137_XVZDF3Z4O.jpg%2F05-524560.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw690_fst_n%26wm%3DY%22&twidth=411&theight=530&opts=17,
