963,결혼 사진 촬영,파스칼 아돌프 장 다냥 부브레,유화,캔버스에 유채(Huile sur toile),,https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src=%22https%3A%2F%2Fdbscthumb-phinf.pstatic.net%2F3329_000_2%2F20140914183204571_1TK4466H7.jpg%2F99-007620.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw690_fst_n%26wm%3DY%22&twidth=690&theight=480&opts=17,
