1252,강물속의 물놀이하는 사람들과 하얀 말,조르주 피에르 쇠라,유화,목판에 유채,,https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src=%22https%3A%2F%2Fdbscthumb-phinf.pstatic.net%2F3329_000_91%2F20141110041611674_YG3BII9N1.jpg%2F2011012514131648.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw690_fst%26wm%3DN%22&twidth=690&theight=447&opts=17,
