1481,비너스와 마르스,산드로 보티첼리,유화,포플러 패널에 템페라와 유채(Tempera and oil on poplar),,https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src=%22https%3A%2F%2Fdbscthumb-phinf.pstatic.net%2F3329_000_53%2F20141001193836637_GRYD3618L.jpg%2FSandro%2BBotticell.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw690_fst%26wm%3DN%22&twidth=690&theight=275&opts=17,
