1563,삼손과 데릴라,페테르 파울 루벤스,유화,목판에 유채(Oil on wood),,https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src=%22https%3A%2F%2Fdbscthumb-phinf.pstatic.net%2F3329_000_53%2F20141001160254271_TGT5YBKCL.jpg%2FPeter%2BPaul%2BRuben.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw690_fst%26wm%3DN%22&twidth=577&theight=530&opts=17,
