1682,욥의 시험 : 욥에게 역병을 들이붓는 사탄,윌리엄 블레이크,유화,마호가니 패널에 템페라,,https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src=%22https%3A%2F%2Fdbscthumb-phinf.pstatic.net%2F3329_000_96%2F20141114001458762_54GP03STB.jpg%2F2011030717100210.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw690_fst%26wm%3DN%22&twidth=690&theight=507&opts=17,
