1700,아기예수와 행운의 여신,피에르 부이용,유화,캔버스에 유채(Huile sur toile),신고전주의,https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src=%22https%3A%2F%2Fdbscthumb-phinf.pstatic.net%2F3329_000_2%2F20140914033912844_0MS7VZQS5.jpg%2F91-001542-02.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw690_fst_n%26wm%3DY%22&twidth=658&theight=530&opts=17,
1701,벨사살왕의 잔치,프란츠 프란켄 2세,유화,동판에 유채(Huile sur cuivre),,https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src=%22https%3A%2F%2Fdbscthumb-phinf.pstatic.net%2F3329_000_91%2F20141110064451375_FP21DXN0H.jpg%2F2011021816314974.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw690_fst_n%26wm%3DY%22&twidth=690&theight=463&opts=17,
