2150,암논에게 겁탈당하는 다말,필립 반 산트보르트,유화,오크 패널에 유채(Oil on oak),,https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src=%22https%3A%2F%2Fdbscthumb-phinf.pstatic.net%2F3329_000_53%2F20141001171756467_TG9LIKIZC.jpg%2FPhilip%2Bvan%2BSantv.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw690_fst%26wm%3DN%22&twidth=434&theight=530&opts=17,
