2463,두 사람이 담배 피고 있는 흡연실 내부,다비드 테니에르 2세,유화,패널에 유채(Huile sur bois),바로크,https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src=%22https%3A%2F%2Fdbscthumb-phinf.pstatic.net%2F3329_000_1%2F20140912004522811_CCC3UF7AU.jpg%2F03-007885.jpg%3Ftype%3Dw690_fst_n%26wm%3DY%22&twidth=379&theight=530&opts=17,
